governanceParametersDescription: Quorum, Voting Period, Timelock Period, Execution Period - these parameters controlling sensible proposal timings and are impacting community participation and speed at which your DAO can run proposals.
governanceTokenDescription: A governance token is an ERC-20 token that grants holders the right to vote and participate in an organization's decision-making process.
governanceERC721TokenDescription: A governance NFT is an ERC-721 token that grants holders the right to vote and participate in an organization's decision-making process.
modulesAndGuardsDescription1: Modules are added contracts that extend a Safe's capabilities.
modulesAndGuardsDescription2: A Freeze Guard is added to all child Safes created on Decent. A Freeze Guard allows the parent Safe to block the child Safe's access to funds and freeze active proposals.
